sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as REST Client<br/>(via ModelMesh Service)
    participant RestProxy as rest-proxy Sidecar<br/>8008/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Marshaler as Custom JSON Marshaler<br/>(in-process)
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh gRPC<br/>localhost:8033/TCP

    Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 1: REST-to-gRPC Inference Request

    Client->>RestProxy: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (TLS optional)<br/>Content-Type: application/json
    activate RestProxy

    RestProxy->>Marshaler: Parse JSON request body
    activate Marshaler
    Note over Marshaler: Flatten nested tensor arrays<br/>Decode base64 BYTES tensors<br/>Convert InferParameter maps
    Marshaler-->>RestProxy: Parsed InferRequest proto
    deactivate Marshaler

    RestProxy->>ModelMesh: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC (TLS optional)<br/>localhost:8033
    activate ModelMesh
    ModelMesh-->>RestProxy: ModelInferResponse
    deactivate ModelMesh

    RestProxy->>Marshaler: Serialize gRPC response
    activate Marshaler
    Note over Marshaler: Reshape tensor data to JSON arrays<br/>Base64-encode BYTES outputs<br/>Convert InferParameter to JSON map
    Marshaler-->>RestProxy: JSON response body
    deactivate Marshaler

    RestProxy-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>application/json
    deactivate RestProxy

    Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 2: Model Metadata Request

    Client->>RestProxy: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (TLS optional)
    activate RestProxy
    RestProxy->>ModelMesh: ModelMetadata RPC<br/>gRPC (TLS optional)<br/>localhost:8033
    activate ModelMesh
    ModelMesh-->>RestProxy: ModelMetadataResponse
    deactivate ModelMesh
    RestProxy-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>application/json
    deactivate RestProxy
